		<p>1.4. Your use of the Minical Service or Minical's Web properties through which the Minical Service is available is also subject to the Minical Privacy Policy in effect at the time of your use, which is incorporated herein as though set forth in full. For the purposes of the Minical Privacy Policy, the Minical Service, any software that you download from Minical to implement any part of the Minical Service and Minical's Web properties through which the Minical Service is available, singly and in combination, constitute part of the &quot;Minical Sites, Products and Services.&quot; You can review the most current version of the Minical Privacy Policy <a href="https://demo.minical.io/auth/show_privacy_policy">here</a>.</p>
		<p>1.5. By signifying your acceptance of this TOS or making any use of the Minical Service, you signify your irrevocable acceptance of this TOS, the Terms of Use and the Minical Privacy Policy in effect at the time of your use. If you are an individual acting as a representative of a corporation or other legal entity which wishes to use the Minical Service, then you represent and agree that you have the authority to accept this TOS, the Terms of Use and the Minical Privacy Policy on behalf of such corporation or other legal entity and that all provisions of this TOS, the Terms of Use and the Minical Privacy Policy will bind that corporation or other legal entity as if it were named in this TOS, the Terms of Use and the Minical Privacy Policy in place of you.</p>
