		</ol>
		<p>6.4. If your account exceeds the maximum appointments/users/month specified in your Minical Paid Plan upgrade screen, Minical will notify you and you will be required to upgrade to maintain service.</p>			
		<p>6.5. Minical will invoice you for any Professional Services fees on a monthly basis and you will pay each such invoice no later than thirty (30) days after receipt.</p>
